                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6 center">
                    <img src="{{ asset('img/demo_application_immo.png') }}" alt="">
                </div>
                <div class="v-spacer"></div>
                <div class="col-md-3 v-mid">
                    <div class="half">
                        <i class="ion-ios-cloud-outline icon"></i>
                        <h2>responsive</h2>
                        <p>Cette application web s'adapter a tous les terminaux: Ordinateurs, Téléphones, Tablettes.</p>
                        
